                  <additions>
                  <list>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
                    <locus target="#5r #25r #48r #85r #102v" facs="005 025 048 085 103">Fols. 5r, 25r, 48r, 85r, 102v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    (etc.) The harags are from the government scriptorium of the late 19th through the early 20th centuries
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a1">
                    <locus target="#23v #47v #84r" facs="024 048 084">Fols. 23v, 47v, 84r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    The scribe, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ ኢየሱስ፡</foreign>, Walda Iyasus, is mentioned
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a2">
                    <locus target="#47v" facs="048">Fol. 47v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Supplication to Mary for blessing: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ለገብርኪ፡ ወልደ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወለፍቅርቱ፡ ወለተ፡ ማርያም፡ ወለውሉዶሙ፡ ኃይለ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቃል፡ ወለ፡ ጸሐፊሁ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ወአባሲ፡ ወልደ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።,</foreign>, “for your servant Walda Yohannes and for his beloved Walatta Maryam and for his children Haila Giyorgis, Gabra Masqal and for his scribe, sinful and wicked Walda Iyasus, for ever and ever, Amen.”
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a3">
                    <locus target="#67v" facs="068">Fol. 67v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Supplication to Jesus Christ for blessing: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ለገብርኪ፡ ወልደ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወለፍቅርቱ፡ ወለተ፡ ማርያም፡ ወለውሉዶሙ፡ ኃይለ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቃል፡ ወለጸሐፊሁ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ወአባሲ፡ ወልደ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</foreign>, “for your servant Walda Yohannes and for his beloved Walatta Maryam and for his children Haila Giyorgis, Gabra Masqal and for his scribe, sinful and wicked Walda Iyasus, for ever and ever, Amen.”
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a4">
                    <locus target="#84r" facs="084">Fol. 84r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Supplication to Saint George for blessing: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ለገብርከ፡ ወልደ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወምስለ፡ ፍቅርቱ፡ ወለተ፡ ማርያም፡ ወለውሉዶሙ፡ ኃይለ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቀል፡ ወለንግሥትነ፡ አስካለ፡ ማርያም፡ ወጸሐፊሁ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ወአባሲ፡ ወልደ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓ፡ አ።</foreign>, “for your servant Walda Iyasus and with his beloved Walatta Maryam and for his children Haila Giyorgis, Gabra Masqal, and for our King Askala Maryam his scribe, sinful and wicked Walda Iyasus, for ever and ever, Amen.”
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a5">
                    <locus target="#114r #114v" facs="114 115">Fols. 114r, 114v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Supplication to Saint Gabri’el for blessing to <foreign xml:lang="gez">ለገብርከ፡ ወልደ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወምስለ፡ ፍቅርቱ፡ ወለተ፡ ማርያም፡ ወምስለ፡ ውሉዶሙ፡ ኃይለ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቀል፡ ወለጸሐፊሁ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ወአባሲ፡ ወልደ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</foreign>, “for your servant Walda Iyasus and with his beloved Walatta Maryam and for his children Haila Giyorgis, Gabra Masqal, and for his scribe, sinful and wicked Walda Iyasus, for ever and ever, Amen.”
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a6">
                    <locus target="#141v" facs="142">Fol. 141v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Supplication to Saint Fanue’l for blessing to <foreign xml:lang="gez">ለገብርከ፡ ወልደ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወምስለ፡ ፍቅርቱ፡ ወለተ፡ ማርያም፡ ወምስለ፡ ውሉዶሙ፡ ኃይለ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቀል፡ ወለጸሐፊሁ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ወአባሲ፡ ወልደ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</foreign>, “for your servant Walda Iyasus and with his beloved Walatta Maryam and for his children Haila Giyorgis, Gabra Masqal, for ever and ever, Amen. And for his scribe, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተስማ፡ ሲፈታ፡</foreign>, Tasama Sifata
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                  </list>
